# /second-opinion skill: per-clone redaction patterns (not the .example template)
.claude/redact-patterns.txt
# /second-opinion skill: codex stderr / debug capture (gitignored — may contain
# code fragments and prompt content that should not enter git history)
.tdd/second-opinion-debug.log
# /second-opinion skill: per-cycle adjudication artifact (regenerated each cycle)
.tdd/second-opinion-completed.md
# require-second-opinion.sh enforcement audit log (local; contains paths only)
.tdd/second-opinion-enforcement.log
# Migration-script audit log (F12; local; contains paths + summary)
.tdd/migration-audit.log

# TDD per-cycle artifacts: gitignored. The active plan and red/green
# proofs reflect a specific in-flight cycle and would ship as stale
# active state to downstream consumers if committed. Templates at
# .tdd/templates/ are the authoritative shipped content; per-cycle
# files are local. (Pack-self bootstrap cycle 2026-05-08 finding.)
.tdd/current-plan.md
.tdd/red-proof.md
.tdd/green-proof.md
.tdd/codex/independent-design.md
.tdd/codex/disposition-matrix.md
.tdd/codex/round*.json
# v1.6.2: schema-context generator output (regenerated by the
# /second-opinion skill on every invocation if older than tdd-config.json)
.tdd/second-opinion/context/
# v1.7.0: per-cycle typed test-edit exception artifact + audit log
.tdd/exceptions/
.tdd/audit/
# v1.9.7: cycle-abandonment durable archive
.tdd/abandoned/
# v1.10.2: per-cycle session-resumption state + active pointer
.tdd/cycles/
.tdd/active

